

modern frontend frameworks

Angular:
- by google
- component-based but complex
- complex architectire and documentation
- robust dependency 

Vue: 
- by Evan and a large community
- simple, flexible, 
- component-based, most straightforward
- support advanced features

React: 
- by facebook
- strong ecosystem, community
- most popular 

feature, 
- virtal Document Object Model: to update the UI
- reconciliation algorithm: efficent way to update DOM
- component-based, unidirectional data flow: 
- JSX: allow to wirte html in Js
